'''阿拉伯高地'''(Arabia Terra)是[[火星|火星]]北部一片辽阔的山地区，它大部分位于[[阿拉伯区|阿拉伯区]]内，有一小部分坐落在[[阿西达里亚海区|阿西达里亚海区]]，最宽处横跨4500公里（2800英里），其中心坐标大致位于{{Coord|21|N|6|E|globe:mars_type:landmark|display=inline,title|notes=<ref>{{gpn|336}}</ref>}} 处，东部和南部地区高出西-北部4公里（13000英尺）。阿拉伯高地遍布陨坑、侵蚀严重，崎岖粗糙的地形表明其年代久远，被认为是该星球上最古老的地形之一。 在众多的陨坑之间，一些峡谷蜿蜒穿过阿拉伯高地，很多流入到与北侧接壤的广袤低地—[[北方大平原|北方大平原]]。

==特征==
阿拉伯高地分布有许多有趣的特征，如该地区的一些[[底座形撞击坑|底座形撞击坑]]就是一个很好的示例。底座形撞击坑的喷出物堆积在周围地形之上，通常形成一圈陡峭的悬崖。喷射物构成的耐蚀层保护了底层材料免受侵蚀<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hirise.lpl.arizona.edu/PSP_008508_1870 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2010-10-28 |archive-date=2016-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161006160507/http://hirise.lpl.arizona.edu/PSP_008508_1870 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；一些陨石坑内坑底上的土墩和岩丘显示出许多的分层结构，这些岩层可能是由火山活动、风或水下沉积所形成<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hirise.lpl.arizona.edu/PSP_009008_1915|title=HiRISE - Layers in Central Mound of Henry Crater. (PSP_009008_1915)|website=hirise.lpl.arizona.edu|access-date=23 March 2018|archive-date=2016-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817022432/http://hirise.lpl.arizona.edu/PSP_009008_1915|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://hirise.lpl.arizona.edu/PSP_004434_1885|title=HiRISE - Layers in Arabia Terra (PSP_004434_1885)|website=hirise.lpl.arizona.edu|access-date=23 March 2018|archive-date=2017-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170905234631/https://hirise.lpl.arizona.edu/PSP_004434_1885|dead-url=no}}</ref>；在吉洪拉沃夫盆地（一座被侵蚀的[[吉洪拉沃夫撞击坑|大陨击坑]]）中观察到了[[暗坡条纹|暗坡条纹]]，这些条纹出现在陡坡上，并随时间而变化，起初呈黑色，可能因大气层中浅色细粒尘埃沉积的缘故，它们的颜色以后会慢慢变浅<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hirise.lpl.arizona.edu/PSP_007531_1935|title=HiRISE - Slope Streaks in Tikhonravov Basin (PSP_007531_1935)|website=hirise.lpl.arizona.edu|access-date=23 March 2018|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816234942/http://hirise.lpl.arizona.edu/PSP_007531_1935|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这些条纹被认为是由沿山坡向下流淌的尘埃所组成，类似于地球上的[[雪崩|雪崩]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hirise.lpl.arizona.edu/PSP_006569_1915|title=HiRISE - Layering and Slope Streaks in Henry Crater (PSP_006569_1915)|website=hirise.lpl.arizona.edu|access-date=23 March 2018|archive-date=2016-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161118015521/http://hirise.lpl.arizona.edu/PSP_006569_1915|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1879年，[[乔凡尼·斯基亚帕雷利|乔凡尼·斯基亚帕雷利]]在地图上用以[[阿拉伯半岛|阿拉伯半岛]]命名的[[反照率特征|反照率特征]]命名了阿拉伯高地。

===可能的构造运动===
1997年对该地区进行的研究，更好地界定了它独特的特征<ref>{{cite journal| title=Arabia Terra, Mars: Tectonic and Palaeoclimatic Evolution of a Remarkable Sector of Martian Lithosphere|last=Anguita|first= F.|date=1997|journal = [[Earth,_Moon,_and_Planets|Earth, Moon, and Planets]]|volume = 77|issue = 1|pages=55–72|bibcode = 1997EM&P...77...55A|doi=10.1023/A:1006143106970|display-authors=etal}}</ref>。一条赤道带被注意到，其所分布的陨石坑地质龄明显小于阿拉伯高地北部和南面的[[诺亚高地|诺亚高地]]，这被解释为是由[[诺亚纪|诺亚纪]]时期，阿拉伯高地下方的火星低地[[隐没带|俯冲]]引发的“早期弧后系统”，这种方式解释了区域性断裂模式，而行星自转不稳定原因假说并不能解释它所具有的伸展构造特征<ref>Brugman, K., B. Hynek, S. Robbins. 2015.  CRATER-BASED TESTS UNLOCK THE MYSTERY OF THE ORIGIN AND EVOLUTION OF ARABIA TERRA, MARS.  Lunar and Planetary Science Conference 2359.pdf</ref>。

===可能的火山活动===
2013年的一项研究表明，阿拉伯高地上的许多陨石坑，包括[[伊甸园山口|伊甸园山口]]<ref name = "USGS1">{{cite web| title = Eden Patera| work = [USGS planetary nomenclature page]| publisher = [[United_States_Geological_Survey|USGS]]| url = http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/15037| access-date = 2013-10-17| archive-date = 2016-12-19| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161219164626/https://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/15037| dead-url = no}}</ref>、幼发拉底山口（Euphrates Patera）<ref name = "USGS2">{{cite web| title = Euphrates Patera| work = [USGS planetary nomenclature page]| publisher = [[United_States_Geological_Survey|USGS]]| url = http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/15038| access-date = 2013-10-17| archive-date = 2016-12-19| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161219164727/https://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/15038| dead-url = no}}</ref>、西洛厄山口（Siloe Patera）<ref name = "USGS3">{{cite web| title = Siloe Patera| work = [USGS planetary nomenclature page]| publisher = [[United_States_Geological_Survey|USGS]]| url = http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/15042| access-date = 2013-10-17| archive-date = 2016-12-19| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161219181450/https://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/15042| dead-url = no}}</ref>且可能还有[[谢梅金撞击坑|谢梅金陨击坑]] <ref name = "USGS4">{{cite web| title = Semeykin| work = [USGS planetary nomenclature page]| publisher = [[United_States_Geological_Survey|USGS]]| url = http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/5423| access-date = 2013-10-17| archive-date = 2017-08-11| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170811010651/https://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/5423| dead-url = no}}</ref>、伊斯墨尼亚山口（Ismenia Patera）<ref name = "USGS5">{{cite web| title = Ismenia Patera| work = [ USGS planetary nomenclature page]| publisher = [[United_States_Geological_Survey|USGS]]| url = http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/15039| access-date = 2013-10-17| archive-date = 2016-12-19| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161219165610/https://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/15039| dead-url = no}}</ref>、俄克修斯山口（Oxus Patera）<ref name = "USGS6">{{cite web| title = Oxus Patera| work = [USGS planetary nomenclature page]| publisher = [[United_States_Geological_Survey|USGS]]| url = http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/15041| access-date = 2013-10-17| archive-date = 2016-12-19| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161219172350/https://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/15041| dead-url = no}}</ref>和俄克修斯凹地等<ref name = "USGS7">{{cite web| title = Oxus Cavus| work = [ USGS planetary nomenclature page]| publisher = [[United_States_Geological_Survey|USGS]]| url = http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/15040| access-date = 2013-10-17| archive-date = 2016-12-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161218003410/https://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/15040| dead-url = no}}</ref>等都代表了诺亚纪晚期到[[赫斯珀里亚纪|赫斯珀里亚纪]]早期<ref name="Michalski2013">{{Cite journal| last1 = Michalski| first1 = J. R.| last2 = Bleacher| first2 = J. E.| doi = 10.1038/nature12482| title = Supervolcanoes within an ancient volcanic province in Arabia Terra, Mars| journal = [[Nature_(journal)|Nature]]| volume = 502| issue = 7469| pages = 47–52| date = 2013|bibcode = 2013Natur.502...47M| pmid=24091975| hdl = 2060/20140011237| hdl-access = free }}</ref>[[超级火山|大规模爆炸式火山喷发]](超级火山)<ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.sciencetimes.com/articles/6663/20150525/european-space-agency-discovered-supervolcano-mars.htm|title= European Space Agency May Have Discovered a Supervolcano on Mars|date= 25 May 2015|author= Brian Wu|publisher= Science Times|accessdate= 2021-08-21|archive-date= 2020-11-08|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201108144250/http://www.sciencetimes.com/articles/6663/20150525/european-space-agency-discovered-supervolcano-mars.htm|dead-url= no}}</ref>形成的[[破火山口|破火山口]]<ref name="Witze2006">{{Cite journal| last1 = Witze| first1 = A.| doi = 10.1038/nature.2013.13857| title = Ancient supervolcanoes revealed on Mars| journal = Nature| date = 2013| doi-access = free }}</ref>，被称为“平原式破火山口复合体”。

这些地势极低的火山特征似乎比[[塔尔西斯|塔尔西斯]]或[[埃律西昂火山区|埃律西昂]]大型[[赫斯珀里亚纪|赫斯珀里亚纪]][[盾状火山|盾状火山]]更古老。例如，伊甸园山口是一块不规则的方圆55×85公里、深达1.8公里的洼地（凹陷），周围是隆起的[[玄武岩|玄武岩]]平原。它包含了三处以弧形陡坡相连的内部洼地，这些洼地有使人联想到泻流[[熔岩湖|熔岩湖]]的阶坡和崩塌的断层，且缺少相同直径和深度[[陨石坑|陨石坑]]该有的撞击起源特征（如坑口不规则、无喷发堆积物、凸起的边缘和中央峰等）<ref name="Michalski2013"/>。

作者认为，与推测的地壳俯冲相比，区域伸展导致的地壳变薄更可能解释火山活动的起源<ref name="Michalski2013"/>。岩浆通过薄地壳快速上升以及由此产生的相对不排气减压，可能解释了更具爆发性的盾状火山喷发都与此类火山口有关。火山喷发在阿拉伯高地上形成了层状沉积，这是广泛分布在火星赤道地区的细粒沉积物之一。 据推断，每座火山口复合体（在其历史上）的总喷发量至少为4600–7200公里<sup>3</sup><ref name="Michalski2013"/>。

==近期的流星撞击==
2002年6月30日至2003年10月5日期间，一颗[[陨石|陨石]]撞击了阿拉伯高地，形成一座直径约22.6米（约74英尺），被浅色和深色喷出物包围的小陨石坑，表明这次撞击切入进浅色地层所在的深度。该陨石坑位于阿拉伯高地内北纬20.6度、西经356.8度附近，[[2001火星奥德赛号|2001火星奥德赛号]][[热辐射成像系统|热辐射成像系统]]红外仪显示了撞击前后的现场情况 
