==河道==
火星上许多地方都有大小不同的河道，至少在某一段时间中，这些河道中很多都可能有水。一项使用[[高分辨率成像科学设备|高分辨率成像科学设备]]图像的研究发现，在阿拉伯高地上发现了超过17000多公里的古河谷<ref>{{cite web|url=http://spaceref.com/mars/fossilized-rivers-suggest-mars-was-once-warm-and-wet.html|title=Fossilized Rivers Suggest Mars Was Once Warm and Wet - SpaceRef|website=spaceref.com|access-date=23 March 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Davis | first1 = J. | last2 = Balme | first2 = M. | last3 = Grindrod | first3 = P. | last4 = Williams | first4 = R. | last5 = Gupta | first5 = S. | year = 2016 | title = Extensive Noachian Fluvial Systems in Arabia Terra: Implications for Early Martian Climate | journal = Geology | volume = 44 | issue = 10| pages = 847–850 | doi = 10.1130/G38247.1| bibcode = 2016Geo....44..847D | doi-access = free }}</ref>。

根据2016年发表在地球物理研究杂志《行星》上的研究，许多古河谷被测定为相对较新的。这些河谷将水流送入到湖泊盆地，有一座昵称为“心湖”的湖泊，其容积与[[安大略湖|安大略湖]]相似<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2016/09/160915142043.htm|title=Some ancient Mars lakes formed long after others|website=sciencedaily.com|access-date=23 March 2018|archive-date=2021-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210828072209/https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2016/09/160915142043.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Wilson | first1 = Sharon A. | last2 = Howard | first2 = Alan D. | last3 = Moore | first3 = Jeffrey M. | last4 = Grant | first4 = John A. | year = 2016 | title = A Cold-Wet Mid-Latitude Environment on Mars during the Hesperian-Amazonian Transition: Evidence from Northern Arabia Valleys and Paleolakes | journal = Journal of Geophysical Research: Planets | volume =  121| issue = 9| pages =  1667–1694| doi = 10.1002/2016JE005052 | bibcode = 2016JGRE..121.1667W }}</ref>。

火星过去的气候可能会让水在表面流动，一段时间以来，人们已经知道，火星自转轴的倾斜或倾角经历过许多巨大的变化，因为它的两颗小卫星缺乏稳定它的引力，无法像月球稳定地球那样，有时火星自转轴的倾斜甚至超过80度<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = name | last2 = Touma | first2 = J. | last3 = Wisdom | first3 = J. | year = 1993 | title = The Chaotic Obliquity of Mars | journal = Science | volume = 259 | issue = 5099| pages = 1294–1297 | bibcode = 1993Sci...259.1294T | doi = 10.1126/science.259.5099.1294 | pmid = 17732249 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Laskar | first1 = J. | last2 = Correia | first2 = A. | last3 = Gastineau | first3 = M. | last4 = Joutel | first4 = F. | last5 = Levrard | first5 = B. | last6 = Robutel | first6 = P. | year = 2004 | title = Long term evolution and chaotic diffusion of the insolation quantities of Mars | url = https://hal.archives-ouvertes.fr/hal-00000860/file/Ma_2004.laskar_prep.pdf | journal = Icarus | volume = 170 | issue = 2 | pages = 343–364 | doi = 10.1016/j.icarus.2004.04.005 | bibcode = 2004Icar..170..343L | access-date = 2021-08-22 | archive-date = 2021-08-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210812063123/https://hal.archives-ouvertes.fr/hal-00000860/file/Ma_2004.laskar_prep.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

